## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="10969-285">O exemplo a seguir cria um <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbParameter> e define algumas de suas propriedades.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="10969-285">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOleDbParameter()  
    Dim parameter As New OleDbParameter("Description", OleDbType.VarChar, 88)  
    parameter.SourceColumn = "Description"  
    parameter.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Current  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateOleDbParameter()   
 {  
    OleDbParameter parameter = new OleDbParameter("Description", OleDbType.VarChar, 88);  
    parameter.SourceColumn = "Description";  
    parameter.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Current;  
 }  
```
